#summary Called when the match is over

{{{
gotMatchOver(finished_player_ids:Array/*int*/)
}}}

`finished_player_ids` contains the `user_id`'s of the players that finished playing.
Note that `finished_player_ids` may contain only a subset of the players (see the TicTacToe demo for such an example).

`got_match_over` may be called if:
  * the player disconnected, choose to lose, agree with the players that he can quit the game, etc. 
  * All the players called [doAllEndMatch].
